lar name in medieval England, normally pronounced ‘Water’."],"variants":[{"name":"Walther","meanings":["from <i>wald</i> ‘rule’ + <i>heri</i> ‘army’; name of the famous medieval minnesinger  Walther von der Vogelweide  (  <i>c.</i>1170– <i>c.</i>1230 )."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Walter Everard was born in 1349, in Mashbury, Essex, England, his father, Ralph John Everard, was 26 and his mother, Mrs Ralph Everard, was 23. He married Elizabeth Mallory in 1374, in Mashbury, Essex, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. He died in 1380, in his hometown, at the age of 31."},"et":{"1349–1380":"1349–1380","1358–1425":"1358–1425","1375–1409":"1375–1409","1323–1349":"1323–1349","1327–Female":"1327–Surnud","1349":"1349","1327":"1327","1425":"1425","1358":"1358","1323":"1323","1375":"1375","1374":"1374","Abt 1348":"umbes 1348","1409":"1409","1380":"1380","Mashbury, Essex, England":"Mashbury, Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Mashbury Essex, England":"Mashbury, Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1349–1380":"1349–1380","1358–1425":"1358–1425","1375–1409":"1375–1409","1323–1349":"1323–1349","1327–Female":"1327–Kuollut","1349":"1349","1327":"1327","1425":"1425","1358":"1358","1323":"1323","1375":"1375","1374":"1374","Abt 1348":"noin 1348","1409":"1409","1380":"1380","Mashbury, Essex, England":"Mashbury, Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Mashbury Essex, England":"Mashbury, Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1349–1380":"1349–1380","1358–1425":"1358–1425","1375–1409":"1375–1409","1323–1349":"1323–1349","1327–Female":"1327–Décédée","1349":"1349","1327":"1327","1425":"1425","1358":"1358","1323":"1323","1375":"1375","1374":"1374","Abt 1348":"environ 1348","1409":"1409","1380":"1380","Mashbury, Essex, England":"Mashbury, Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Mashbury Essex, England":"Mashbury, Essex, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Walter Everard est né en 1349, à Mashbury, Essex, Angleterre, son père, Ralph John Ever